:

*Problem je da se ne možeš više vratiti nazad. (The problem is that you can't go back anymore.)
*Razmišljao sam o problemu kako da ga rešim. (I was thinking about the problem of how to solve it.)
*Neko je navodno imao problem sa automobilom. (Someone allegedly had a problem with the car.)
*Moj izazov bio je da rešim problem. (My challenge was to solve the problem.)